FuncDef: This command specifies the interworking function that should be applied for packets that ingress or egress SAPs that are part of an Apipe service.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies Frame Relay to ATM Network Interworking (FRF.5).

ExtraInfo: Default: none (Interworking must be configured before adding a Frame-Relay SAP to an Apipe service.)
